#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Static** pages, such as the homepage or any :ref:`custom-created <website/"
"pages/page_creation>`, contain fixed content that does not change "
"dynamically. You can manually create these pages, define their URLs, and "
"adapt their :ref:`properties <website/pages/page_management>` as needed. "
